body_html:
Thanks @marksandler2

I tried your code and it works fine. we can evaluate all output of the FusedBatchNorm in your code.

It seems the frozen graph has a compatibility issue with latest TensorFlow.
Only TF1.8 or earlier version can correctly evaluate outputs of the fused batchnorm in the frozen graph.
